Welcome to this lecture on 'Mathematics for Machine Learning.' Today, we'll explore the critical mathematical foundations required to truly understand and apply machine learning. Based on the acclaimed textbook by Deisenroth, Faisal, and Ong, this session will highlight how complex mathematical concepts are made accessible and directly relevant to core ML algorithms, bridging the gap between theoretical math and practical machine learning applications.

