The textbook caters to two main audiences: those with a mathematical background can use the derivations as a starting point for advanced ML texts, while those new to the math build intuition and practical experience. Every chapter includes worked examples and exercises, complemented by online programming tutorials, ensuring a comprehensive and hands-on learning journey for all.

